Host *
  ConnectTimeout 5
  ConnectionAttempts 3

  Compression yes

  AddressFamily inet
  ExitOnForwardFailure yes
  StrictHostKeyChecking accept-new

  ControlMaster auto
  ControlPersist 5m

  TCPKeepAlive yes
  ServerAliveInterval 1
  ServerAliveCountMax 10

  HostkeyAlgorithms +ssh-rsa
  PubkeyAcceptedAlgorithms +ssh-rsa
